column102: Ncf: Number of failed test cases that cover the rule
Nus: Number of successful test cases that cover the rule
Ncs: Number of successful test cases that cover the rule
Nus: number of successful test cases that do not cover the rule
Nc: total number of test cases that cover the rule
Nu:total number of test cases that do not cover the rule

column2: SrcPackage.allInstances()->forAll(p | TrgERModel.allInstances()->exists(e | p.name = e.name and p.ownedElements->forAll(class | e.entities->exists(entity | entity.name = class.name and class.ownedProperty->forAll(prop | (not prop.complexType.oclIsUndefined() and not prop.isContainment) implies entity.features-> select(f|f.oclIsTypeOf(TrgWeakReference)) -> exists(f | f.name = prop.name))))))
